```

#### Facebook (`src/auth-facebook/auth-facebook.service.ts`)
- Validates token via `/debug_token` endpoint
- Verifies token belongs to the app
- Fetches user profile from `v23.0/me` endpoint with fields: `id, last_name, email, first_name`

#### Apple (`src/auth-apple/auth-apple.service.ts`)
```typescript
async getProfileByToken(loginDto: AuthAppleLoginDto): Promise<SocialInterface> {
